quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  57,19,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko nn …ìe senndaali …óum, ko …ìen woni sifor…ìe goonguugol. Sahimbinaa…ìe …ìen ka Joomi mun, hino woodani …ìen mbarjaari ma…ì…ìe maranaa…ìe ndi …ìen e annoora ndaygiroya…óo yeeso e √±aame ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darngal. ∆Åen non yeddu…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe woni e fennugol Aayeeje jippinaa…óe …óen e Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, ko …ìen woni yim…ìe Jahiimi ngen. ∆Åe naatoyat e magge √ëalnde Darngal, ko …ìe luttata poomaa."
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde …óam nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru …ìalli e welo-welo …ìer…óe, e cu…óaari mon, e mantagol hakkunde mon fii laamu e dakamme, …ìurodira …óuu…óugol jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe. ∆äum no wa'i wa to…ìo haawnayngo remoo…ìe …ìen e pu…ói mun, refti …óin pu…ói kecci yoora ko yaawi, yi'aa …óum an ndaaroowo on, hino wonta ko soy…ói, refti Allah muncita fii mun wonta kelon kelon. Hino ka laakara, lette sa…ótu…óe wonannde heefer…ìe …ìen e naafiqi'en, e yaafuyee immmorde ka Allah wonannde bakkatuuji jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen e welayee Makko. Awa …óam nguurdam aduna wonaali, si wanaa dakamme lannoowo. Kala su…ìii…óo on dakamme lannoowo e hoore neema laakara on, haray on …óon ko sooyu…óo koomtaa…óo."
  57,21,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, adondiree e golle mo∆¥∆¥e …óe da√±irton yaafaneede junuubi ka Joomi mon: immorde e tuubugol maa kala golle …ìa…ótor…óe Allah ekw, e no he…ìiron Allah mo yaajeendi mun wa'i wa yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama …ìen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ngal ke…ìal ko …ìural Allah ngal O okkata mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Allah ko Jom …ìural mawnungal e dow jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen."
  57,22,"Bone woo he…ìataa yim…ìe …ìen ka leydi immorde e kokke m. kw. wanaa ko memata …ìe e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa …óum tabitananooma ka Alluwal reenaanagl, ado Men tagude ndee tagoore. Pellet, …óum ko ko newanii Allah."
  57,23,"∆äum ko fii wata onon …ìee yim…ìe wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, hara kadi on weltoraali neema ko O neemini e mon kon fantinon. Pellet, Alla yi…óaa kala √±aa∆¥oroowo mantoro ko Allah okki mo kon e hoore yim…ìe …ìen."
  57,24,"∆Åen wuddiroo…ìe ko …ìe haani okkude kon, …ìe yamira kadi yim…ìe …ìen nguddam, ko hayru…ìe. Kala …óuurnii…óo e …óoftagol Allah, …óum ko kanko lorrata, wanaa doo Allah. Pellet, Allah kan ko Galo Mo hatonjinaa e …óoftaare jeyaa…ìe Makko, Yettinii…óo e kala fiyaaku."